---
import BaseLayout from '../../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about the mission and history of the Joe Rossi Hall of Fame." canonicalPath="/about/">
  <PageHero title="About The Joe Rossi Hall of Fame" intro="Honoring the individuals whose dedication, hard work, and contributions have made a lasting impact on the game of baseball." />
  <section class="section"><article class="container surface about-story">
    <p>The Joe Rossi Hall of Fame was founded in 1989 to recognize the lifelong contributions of Joe Rossi—a leader and mentor whose dedication helped shape high school umpiring in Colorado.</p>

    <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
    <p>Our mission is to recognize and celebrate individuals who have made a difference in high school umpiring. By honoring their achievements, JRHOF aims to inspire future generations of leaders, mentors, and community stewards.</p>

    <figure>
      <img src="/images/joe_rossi_first_pitch.jpeg" alt="Joe Rossi at Coors Field with Dinger and a young baseball fan" width="800" height="600" />
      <figcaption>Joe Rossi at Coors Field.</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <h2>History</h2>
    <p>The Hall of Fame preserves Joe Rossi's legacy alongside the stories of others who strengthened baseball and its officiating community. Since its founding, it has continued to recognize people whose leadership, judgment, and service made a lasting contribution to the game.</p>

    <h2>Inductees</h2>
    <p>Inductees are chosen for their contributions to high school umpiring and baseball in Colorado. Their biographies preserve the history of the people who served, taught, mentored, and supported the game.</p>

    <h2>Looking Ahead</h2>
    <p>JRHOF remains committed to preserving its history and honoring individuals who have contributed to baseball in Colorado.</p>

    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <p>Supporters can be part of the Hall of Fame legacy by attending events, contributing historical materials, or helping preserve the stories of inductees.</p>
    <div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/inductees/">Explore Inductees</a><a class="button button-secondary" href="/contact/">Contact JRHOF</a></div>
  </article></section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-story { max-width: 960px; }
  .about-story > p:first-child { font-size: 1.08rem; }
  .about-story h2 { margin: 2rem 0 .65rem; }
  .about-story figure { margin: 1.75rem 0 2rem; }
  .about-story img { display: block; width: 100%; max-height: 520px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 5px; }
  .about-story figcaption { padding-top: .5rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .about-story h2 { margin-top: 1.6rem; } }
</style>
